_sText:
I started playing gun game for the first time years ago on a server that played mostly custom glass maps.  I've always thought that I had the most fun with gun game during those days, but I thought the one flaw with glass maps was how everyone committed suicide much too often. In Funneltimes, there is no suicide area; instead, players are teleported elsewhere.

Hope you enjoy it

- PrestO
